    C1 --> D3</pre><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">价值分布：</strong></p>
        <section style="text-align: left; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-weight: 400; background-color: rgba(250, 249, 245, 1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01); border-radius: 25px; padding: 12px 12px; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto;">
          <table class="preview-table" style="color: #3f3f3f; margin-top: 0 !important;">
