      <h3 class="h3" data-heading="true" style="padding-left: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #A93226; border-radius: 2px; margin: 0 8px 10px; color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.2;">5.2 职业机会</h3><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">紧缺岗位：</strong></p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• Agent 架构师（设计多代理系统）</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 提示工程专家（优化代理行为）</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 代理安全工程师（防注入、防越狱）</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 向量数据库专家（高性能检索）</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">技能栈建议：</strong></p><pre class="hljs code__pre" style="color: #24292e; background: #fff; font-size: 90%; overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 8px; box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 0 !important;"><span class="mac-sign" style="display: flex; padding: 10px 14px 0;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" width="45px" height="13px" viewBox="0 0 450 130">
